originalText.text: Bianca is a wonderful Pilates teacher. She gauges carefully how best to meet your objectives and what you need, overall and in each session. She is very observant and careful, as well as imaginative. She enjoys what she does and wants you to.

originalText.text: Bianca is a very knowledge, professional and wonderfully fun pilates teacher. I highly recommend her and look forward to working with her again once my schedule calms down.

originalText.text:
Bianca is a terrific Pilates teacher. She is extremely knowledgeable about human anatomy and how one part of the body affects another. If you are a beginner, she makes the world of Pilates friendly.
Because she is also a dancer and choreographer, she will have one movement follow another to assist one's own movement and recovery. She watches you carefully and thoughtfully; she illustrates and corrects positions and movement for best results. And she has a wonderful sense of humor. I had no idea Pilates could be so much fun.
Because of the classes I have taken with her, I no longer have lower back or hip pain, I stand straighter, and am definitely stronger and more flexible.
I highly recommend her private studio classes for the best Pilates experience.

originalText.text: Bia is an amazing and gifted teacher. She is well educated and experienced in Pilates and dance and uses her knowledge to give assessment and feedback in a really positive and fun way. No matter where she is teaching or whether it is a private or group class she is totally present and helps you to get the most out of your session. I have learn and benefit so much from working with her.
